### Day 8 — `TODAY_TASK.md`

```markdown
# Day 8 — TODAY_TASK.md
## Goal
Add ingestion framework skeleton (dispatcher + locking + plugin interface) with a mock source plugin.

## Files allowed to change/create
- utility-explorer-api/src/main/java/**
- utility-explorer-api/src/test/java/**
- PROJECT_STATE.md

## Requirements
- Dispatcher runs on a fixed tick (env var INGESTION_TICK_SECONDS).
- Per-source lock prevents concurrent runs.
- Mock plugin writes deterministic facts and logs a source_run.
- Must be idempotent (re-run doesn’t create duplicate fact_value rows).

## Acceptance checks
- Enable ingestion and confirm source_run rows created
- Run twice → no duplicates in fact_value PK

## Stop and ask if
- Locking strategy is unclear (choose Postgres advisory lock if available; if uncertain, ask).

## End-of-day output
- How to enable/disable ingestion
- Update PROJECT_STATE.md
```

