```markdown
# Day 13 — TODAY_TASK.md (Copilot v1)
## Goal
Implement read-only Copilot endpoint and UI panel (minimal).

## Files allowed to change/create
- utility-explorer-api/src/main/java/**
- utility-explorer-api/src/test/java/**
- utility-explorer-ui/src/**
- PROJECT_STATE.md

## Requirements
- /copilot/query requires X-API-Key.
- Implement QuerySpec internally and validate strictly.
- Implement one query type: INTERSECTION using latest common period (only using existing data).
- UI panel: input question, display result table + citations, “highlight on map” optional.

## Acceptance checks
- Without API key -> 401
- With key and data -> OK response
- With missing data -> INSUFFICIENT_DATA

## Stop and ask if
- QuerySpec semantics are ambiguous (ask before expanding).

## End-of-day output
- Example question + response
- Update PROJECT_STATE.md
```

